<s> Any statistics are likely to underestimate the low end of the market because there will be no commercial interests to collect the statistics and many people will mis-represent their browser to web sites because of real and imagined fears that the site will discriminate against them if they give its true identity, rather than that of one of the big2 (this actually happened to early IEs, so IE actually identifies as Netscape (Mozilla), with a comment that it is IE!).  </s>
